Sentece: A sensitivity of 20 ng/ml for both testolactone and 4,5-dihydrotestolactone is easily achieved using only 0.5 ml of sample.
Title: Quantitation of testolactone and 4,5-dihydrotestolactone in plasma and urine using high-performance liquid chromatography.
Name: Testolactone

Sentece: Mean recoveries for testolactone and its metabolite are 95.0% and 81.8%, respectively, and the mean coefficient of variation of the procedure is 3.5% for the drug and 7.1% for the metabolite.
